headline: Raymond James lifts FactSet rating on cheaper valuation, signs of revenue rebound
summary: Investing.com -- Raymond James upgraded FactSet Research Systems to Market perform from Underperform, saying the market-data provider’s shares already reflect most of the competitive and budgeting pressures that slowed growth over the past two years.
